reviewText: Thanks for the speedy shipment. Exactly what I wanted.
good information, don't expect much more than a history lesson and perhaps some great shots of Ireland.
An excellent short history of Ireland.  Well told!!

The only reason I gave it three stars was because I didn't like it as much as I was hoping. I actually found the entire movie on YouTube and was hoping it wasn't the DVD I ordered. I haven't watched the whole thing yet.
Fantastic story, great pictures, and just enough dialogue to keep you informed and not bored. It is a good companion piece to the book.

All you really need to know about Ireland in a comprehensive and thorough video.
Much easier to comprehend than other videos.
